—ظSarchive/external_nushell_repo_backup/nushell.github.io/commands/docs/random_uuid.mdظ@f9d8a8992b5e621be936cfa5d095a4ceac084ab894c40a40371f4f67b8eed3f1²title: random uuid‘¨Examplesع|Generate a random uuid v4 string (default).
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> random uuid


```
Generate a uuid v1 string (timestamp-based).
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> random uuid -v 1 -m 00:11:22:33:44:55


```
Generate a uuid v3 string (namespace with MD5).
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> random uuid -v 3 -n dns -s example.com


```
Generate a uuid v4 string (random).
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> random uuid -v 4


```
Generate a uuid v5 string (namespace with SHA1).
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> random uuid -v 5 -n dns -s example.com


```
Generate a uuid v7 string (timestamp + random).
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> random uuid -v 7


```
